# Trojan-Go Proxy Client
# Version: 1.2.0
# Upstream (maintained fork): https://github.com/kis1yi/trojan-go
# Release page: https://github.com/kis1yi/trojan-go/releases/tag/v1.2.0
# Release asset: trojan-go-windows-amd64.zip
# Extract trojan-go.exe into this directory.
#
# Companion geo data files (downloaded by CI, not committed):
#   geoip.dat    — from https://github.com/v2fly/geoip/releases/latest
#   geosite.dat  — from https://github.com/v2fly/domain-list-community/releases/latest
#                  (CI downloads dlc.dat and saves it as geosite.dat)
# Both are placed alongside trojan-go.exe so trojan-go's default
# router.geoip / router.geosite paths resolve.
